text: Nikita Nguyen (born January 31, 1996) known professionally as Nikita Dragun, is an American YouTuber, make-up artist, and model. ==Life== Nikita Dragun was born in Belgium and went to high school in Virginia. She is of Vietnamese and Mexican descent. She came out as a trans woman when she was a teenager. In several of Dragun's YouTube videos, she has spoken openly about her transition. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:American YouTubers Category:American models Category:Entertainers from Virginia Category:American LGBT people Category:LGBT models Category:Transgender women Category:LGBT businesspeople Category:Businesspeople from Virginia
